Goodyear Tire and Rubber Co said itwill receive about 588 mln dlrs in cash from Loral Corp &lt;LOR>for the business of Goodyear Aerospace Corp.    Goodyear said the previously announced acquisition by Loralis expected to be completed March 13. When Loral announced thetransaction January 12, the company said it was paying 640 mlndlrs for Goodyear Aerospace.    Goodyear said the price it will receive is afteradjustments for such items as pension and benefits provision,allocation of liabilities and asset valuations. Last yearGoodyear Aerospace had revenues of 695 mln dlrs.                Reuter&#3;